DIRECTORIES
	Ne.sim
		: scripts used to perform simulation in Figure 1C and 1D (high recombination rate)
	Ne.sim.2
		: scripts used to perform simulation in Figure 1C and 1D (low recombination rate)
	Bacteria.sim
		: scripts used to perform simulation in Figure 2
	visualization
		: scripts to generate Figure 1 and Figure 2

SCRIPTS
	
		: a script used to perform simulation in Figure 1B
	human.collectres.pl
		: a script used to collect the results generated by humans.sim.pl
	Bacteria.collectres.pl
		: a script used to collect the results generated by Bacteria.sim/j*


